publicationStmt.publisher: Manuscripta.se: A Digital Catalogue of Manuscripts in Sweden

binding.p: The manuscript is stored in cardboard boxes.

history.provenance: Owned in the latter half of the 17th c. by Catalina de Haro, marquess de Heliche. She sold the manuscript in 1690 to Johan Gabriel Sparwenfeldt (1655-1727) when he was in Spain.
history.acquisition: Donated by Sparwenfeldt to the Royal Library in 1706.

supportDesc.foliation: Foliation in red ink written in the upper left corner.
